{"tid":780330,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不能錯過的女友！唐詩詠 女漢子上身","createTime":"2018-08-15T05:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T07:28:08.000Z","uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d0fbe19253de75dfaa2469ddbf418ed2c1233f9b","tid":780330,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1yO79mDumHD9XXizPCx3Z9StLvSHLCW30\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1yO79mDumHD9XXizPCx3Z9StLvSHLCW30&h=65abc747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>不能錯過的女友！唐詩詠 女漢子上身</strong><br />\n<br />\n同洪永城分手大半年，個個都希望有不能錯過的女友之稱嘅唐詩詠搵到幸福，但偏偏未有著落，個個都擔心詩詠點解仲未搵到主好人家，其實睇落外表柔弱，覺得唐詩詠需要人照顧都係啲fans一廂情願諗法，實情人哋不知幾獨立，而且一個人過得不知幾硬淨！<br />\n<br />\n撰文：東方新地｜圖片：新傳媒圖片庫、<br />\n<br />\n<strong>唐詩詠 由朝忙到晚</strong><br />\n<br />\n唔使拍拖，不過要開劇又開咗蛋糕店做老闆，時間可能已經唔多夠用。日前詩詠就示範要開工，就去咗做gym保持住最佳狀態，閒時約閨密聚吓、或行山，生活健康到不得了，總之就由朝到晚排滿晒。重點係冇個男友喺身邊照顧，詩詠仲將外套紮喺腰間、自己一手拎起大大袋衣物，如女漢子上身，睇怕習慣咗自己事自己做喎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1PBEmfZXe_xY0fm1gC63fn_Fg62khDu_E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1PBEmfZXe_xY0fm1gC63fn_Fg62khDu_E&h=f7fdae71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無論幾咁忙，keep住副body係好重要，日前唐詩詠素顏現身，一個人上咗樓上gym room做運動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1g3TdvrAak3jSIbxsqyNyoAnP0S1gCJ8O\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1g3TdvrAak3jSIbxsqyNyoAnP0S1gCJ8O&h=984dd748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一向瘦削兼身冇幾両肉嘅詩詠離開健身室時除去外套，一個人拎起兩大袋衣物，證明瘦削唔代表柔弱，一樣可以係女漢子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1tBmL4yMtGrP5iGdTTbczm-pzGZz_VI27\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1tBmL4yMtGrP5iGdTTbczm-pzGZz_VI27&h=6590e8e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唐詩詠平時keep住做gym又行山，生活健康，更練得一身好線條，唔係外表睇嚟咁潺弱㗎！<br />\n<br />\n唐詩詠叫其他「鐵馬家族」成員快啲結婚，等佢可以再去峇里玩！但其實佢哋中間係得唐詩詠、黃嘉樂、唐文龍同馬國明未結婚咋喎！唔知佢喺度催緊邊個呢？<br />\n<br />\n來源 source: <a href=\"http://www.orientalsunday.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientalsunday.hk&d=bzEgjJDypzABWqFO%2B20nl9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=0e9f2650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orientalsunday.hk</a><br />\n+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++<br />\n又吹捧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c927558b836c8522c87b537a946165d3d1275f84","tid":780330,"uid":150053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64f0c249affd402d989888bc2dd4b895b3876b8","tid":780330,"uid":82917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/134210_e90d43c5447e6f90814e6453c0bcfc60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F134210_e90d43c5447e6f90814e6453c0bcfc60.png&h=a37a7f6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95475668d94ddd538d5f7dce4ad69c19109ca382","tid":780330,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:45:21.000Z","msg":"比人調教左咁多年，邊個接得落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c91214f9c46c52e761a413db16276cd6ea6d56","tid":780330,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b64f0c249affd402d989888bc2dd4b895b3876b8","tid":780330,"uid":82917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/134210_e90d43c5447e6f90814e6453c0bcfc60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F134210_e90d43c5447e6f90814e6453c0bcfc60.png&h=a37a7f6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:00:00.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/asse